name: Barb G.
review: Great product at a great price. I also use the brush everyday after applying my eyebrow pencil.

name: Hairlicious
review: Worth every penny!

name: KiraJ07
review: This helps me shape my brows and trim away any strays.  The brush is great too.  Sometimes, it's difficult for me to angle the scissors for a proper trim but I don't think this has anything to do with the design.

name: tundrafoodie
review: Nice cushioning for fingers on scissors.

name: Ice Skater
review: The  scissors are super sharp and very light. The grips inside the handles are great, they help take a firm hold. The brush is very soft, more than I expected. The set made the trimming of my eyebrows quick and easy. They're thin enough to be allow you to easily see how much you're trimming off your eyebrow.

name: Carrie
review: Easy to use. I like it

name: Laceys14
review: This is the perfect brow set.  I love the brush. And the scissors is so precise, very sharp. Perfect size too! I love it!

name: orangesky
review: Don't waste your money on more expensive scissors.  These will do the trick just fine.  I like Revlon for all of my grooming tools.

name: Suzanne the 40 something
review: Scissors are super sharp and small enough for precision facial hair trimming.

name: Mich
review: Love the quality on the scissors.  Cuts great!  The brow brush is also pretty good quality. Tames my crazy brows really well.

name: G
review: Good product.

name: HeidiHeartsSkincare
review: These scissors are great. For the price you can't beat them. They come with a pretty red grip on the finger loops of the scissors. Which was great for me because I'm clumsy and it prevents slipping. They are very sharp and easy to get around the curves of my eyebrows. I could even use these to trim baby hairs or split ends. I didn't care much for the spoolie that came with them. It was kind of flimsy, so if you're buying these for the spoolie. Then I suggest you move on to another product. If you're buying them for the scissors then I definitely suggest these.

name: rpm
review: Easy to use and get the job done.

name: Sienna
review: I have to keep up with my eyebrows constantly. I was spending so much money on getting them waxed because I was afraid I'd destroy my eyebrows. It took a little practice to find the best way to use it but I'm so happy that I took the chance. I use this set a lot and I'd recommend it to anyone.

name: Kay the mua
review: Cuts nicely and accurately.

name: Hannah
review: I use it every morning and night to reshape my brows and change growth pattern.

name: Abby
review: I purchased this product because my previous Revlon spiral  brush that I had for years was beginning to get worn from use.  The quality of the new one is not even close to the older one.  The bristles on the new one are shorter and not as sturdy and will never hold up for long term use like the older one.  In addition, I did not need the scissors and only purchase the product because I needed to replace my spiral brush.  The brush used to be sold separately but is now sold with the scissors as a set.  I cannot recommend this product.

name: Undertaking
review: I mainly bought this duo for the spool brush, but the scissors are excellent. Super sharp and easy to maneuver. The spool brush is great as well. Takes the unruly mess I have easily. I use the spool every day.

name: Mimi
review: I use this product daily.

name: hewwogillian
review: This set is perfect for eyebrow grooming. The scissors are easy to hold and work great.
